<html>
<body style="background:#ececec; margin:1em; padding:1em;">
	<div style="margin:1em; background:#fff; padding:0.5em;">
		<h2>Forgot Password Notification.</h2>
		<p>You've chosen to reset your password, click here or copy this url (<%- user.attributes.reset_token %>) to reset your password</p>

		<p> 
			If you did not request your password to be reset please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.
		</p>
		<p>
			Login with your email or username (<a href='http://example.com/<%= user.username %>' target='_blank'><%= user.username %></a>) at 
			<a href='http://example.com/' target='_blank'>
			http://example.com/
			</a> 
		</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>